API_Description: Embeds a color profile as a PDF/X Output Intent (see the PDF Reference ).

outputIntentColorSpace.description: A string containing the description of the profile to use for the output intent. A list of available color profiles can be obtained from the printColorProfiles property of the app object.

Examples:
Embed a color profile.

```
this.embedOutputIntent("U.S. Sheetfed Coated v2")
```
